Uses of Package
Catalano.Imaging

  • Packages that use Catalano.Imaging 
    Package Description
    Catalano.Imaging
    The Catalano.Imaging contains base class for manipulation of pixels.
    Catalano.Imaging.ActiveContour.Ovuscule  
    Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent
    The Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent namespace contains base classes for share data among the theads.
    Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent.Filters
    The Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters running in parallel.
    Catalano.Imaging.Corners
    The Catalano.Imaging.Corners contains Interest point detectors (i.e Harris, Susan and FREAK).
    Catalano.Imaging.Corners.FREAK
    The Catalano.Imaging.Corners.FREAK contains classes used in Fast Retina Keypoint (FREAK).
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters.
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Artistic
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Artistic namespace contains collection classes, which provide different artistic filters.
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Integral
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Integral namespace contains filters, which internally use integral image.
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Photometric
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters.Photometric namespace contains filters for photometric normalization used in face recognition tasks.
    Catalano.Imaging.Parsers
    The Catalano.Imaging.Parsers namespace contains support of format images.
    Catalano.Imaging.Texture
    The Catalano.Imaging.Texture namespace contains collection classes, which provide texture image retrieval.
    Catalano.Imaging.Texture.BinaryPattern
    The Catalano.Imaging.Texture.BinaryPattern namespace contains collection classes, which provide texture binary pattern based.
    Catalano.Imaging.Tools
    The Catalano.Imaging.Tools namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image moments, analysis textures.
    Catalano.Vision
    The Catalano.Vision contains filters used for sequence of images.
    Catalano.Vision.Detection  
    Catalano.Vision.SpatioTemporal
    The Catalano.Vision.SpatioTemporal contains filters in spatio temporal for image processing.
    Catalano.Vision.Temporal
    The Catalano.Vision.Temporal contains temporal filters for image processing.
    Catalano.Vision.Tools
